title: The Dark Tower III - The Waste Lands (128kbps)
description: This is the third book in the Dark Tower series by Stephen King, and is read by Frank Muller (he read the first four books in this series). I have seen this book in other places, but they are all read by the author. Though a great author, he has a very annoying voice. Frank Muller does a MUCH better job. Please seed this file because I cannot seem to find it anywhere (I originally downloaded it on the now defunct Demonoid).
